### AI-102 REST API Examples
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Replace {{endpoint}} and {{apiKey}} with your values
### Or create a .env file with these variables

### ============================================
### Detect Language — Azure AI Language
### Module 1, Lab 1.1
### ============================================

@endpoint = {{$dotenv AI_SERVICES_ENDPOINT}}
@apiKey = {{$dotenv AI_SERVICES_KEY}}

### Detect language
POST {{endpoint}}/text/analytics/v3.2-preview.2/languages
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "documents": [
    { "id": "1", "text": "Bonjour tout le monde" },
    { "id": "2", "text": "Hello world" },
    { "id": "3", "text": "Hola mundo" }
  ]
}
